<paragraph blockId="21.[794,1419,762,1747]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">
The genus 
<taxonomicName authority="Wittmer, 1949" authorityName="Wittmer" authorityYear="1949" box="[964,1267,762,787]" class="Insecta" family="Cantharidae" genus="Hyponotum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[964,1095,762,787]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">Hyponotum</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Wittmer, W." box="[1104,1267,762,787]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" pagination="215 - 222" refId="ref19618" refString="Wittmer, W. 1949. 7. Beitrag zur Kenntnis der neotropischen Malacodermata. Revista de la Sociedad EntomolOgica Argentina, 14: 215 - 222." type="journal article" year="1949">Wittmer, 1949</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
was erected as distinct from the genus 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Constantin &amp; Chaboo" baseAuthorityYear="2016" box="[1102,1242,794,819]" class="Insecta" family="Cantharidae" genus="Plectonotum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1102,1242,794,819]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">Plectonotum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in the reduced or absent pronotal bead, and in the simple pygidium, without apico-lateral protuberances. Wittmer designated 
<taxonomicName authority="Pic, 1926" authorityName="Pic" authorityYear="1926" box="[870,1273,890,915]" class="Insecta" family="Cantharidae" genus="Plectonotum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="albocinctum">
<emphasis box="[870,1158,890,915]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">Plectonotum albocinctum</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Pic, M." box="[1169,1273,890,915]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" pagination="25 - 28" refId="ref19506" refString="Pic, M. 1926. Malacodermes exotiques. L'Echange, 42 (424), Hors-texte: 25 - 28." type="journal article" year="1926">Pic, 1926</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
as the 
<typeStatus box="[1366,1417,890,915]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">type</typeStatus>
species of 
<emphasis box="[926,1063,922,947]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Wittmer" authorityYear="1949" box="[926,1059,922,947]" class="Insecta" family="Cantharidae" genus="Hyponotum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Hyponotum</taxonomicName>
,
</emphasis>
transferred 
<taxonomicName authority="Pic, 1928" authorityName="Pic" authorityYear="1928" class="Insecta" family="Cantharidae" genus="Plectonotum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="grandicolle">
<emphasis box="[1215,1366,922,947]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">P. grandicolle</emphasis>
Pic, 1928
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Pic, 1926" authorityName="Pic" authorityYear="1926" box="[861,1077,954,979]" class="Insecta" family="Cantharidae" genus="Plectonotum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ruficolle">
<emphasis box="[861,970,954,979]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">P. ruficolle</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Pic, M." box="[975,1077,954,979]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" pagination="25 - 28" refId="ref19506" refString="Pic, M. 1926. Malacodermes exotiques. L'Echange, 42 (424), Hors-texte: 25 - 28." type="journal article" year="1926">Pic, 1926</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Pic, 1928" authorityName="Pic" authorityYear="1928" box="[1085,1366,954,979]" class="Insecta" family="Cantharidae" genus="Plectonotum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="violaceipenne">
<emphasis box="[1085,1259,954,979]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">P. violaceipenne</emphasis>
Pic, 1928
</taxonomicName>
, and 
<taxonomicName authority="Wittmer, 1945" authorityName="Wittmer" authorityYear="1945" box="[794,1074,986,1011]" class="Insecta" family="Cantharidae" genus="Plectonotum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="kuscheli">
<emphasis box="[794,906,986,1011]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">P. kuscheli</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Wittmer, W." box="[913,1074,986,1011]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" pagination="313 - 326" refId="ref19550" refString="Wittmer, W. 1945. Nuevos Cantharidae (Col.) (4 º contribucion al conocimiento de los Malacodermata neotropicos). Revista de la Sociedad EntomolOgica Argentina, 12: 313 - 326." type="journal article" year="1945">Wittmer, 1945</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Wittmer" authorityYear="1949" box="[1114,1245,986,1011]" class="Insecta" family="Cantharidae" genus="Hyponotum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1114,1245,986,1011]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">Hyponotum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and described 
<emphasis box="[794,1054,1018,1043]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Wittmer" authorityYear="1949" box="[794,1050,1018,1043]" class="Insecta" family="Cantharidae" genus="Hyponotum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mimicum">Hyponotum mimicum</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
Later 
<bibRefCitation author="Wittmer, W." box="[1152,1332,1018,1043]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" pagination="247 - 257" refId="ref19646" refString="Wittmer, W. 1950. 9. Beitrag zur Kenntnis der neotropischen Malacodermata (Col.). Revista de Entomologia, Rio de Janeiro, 21 (1 - 2): 247 - 257." type="journal article" year="1950">Wittmer (1950</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Wittmer, W." box="[1356,1414,1018,1043]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" pagination="187 - 188" refId="ref19684" refString="Wittmer, W. 1951. Nuevos Cantharidae de la Cordillera de los Andes (Coleoptera). (11. Contribucion al conocimiento de los Malacodermata neotropicales). Revista Chilena de Entomologia, 1: 187 - 188." type="journal article" year="1951">1951</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Wittmer, W." box="[794,853,1050,1075]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" pagination="67 - 71" refId="ref19725" refString="Wittmer, W. 1957. Notas sobre algunos Cantharidae de Chile (1) (Coleoptera). Revista Chilena de Entomologia, 5: 67 - 71." type="journal article" year="1957">1957</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Wittmer, W." box="[863,921,1050,1075]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" pagination="62 - 65" refId="ref19790" refString="Wittmer, W. 1980. 36. Beitrag zur Kenntnis der neotropischen Cantharidae (Col.). Mitteillungen der Entomologische Gesellschaft Basel, N. F., 30: 62 - 65." type="journal article" year="1980">1980</bibRefCitation>
) described eight new species belonging to this genus and transferred others from 
<emphasis box="[1271,1418,1082,1107]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Constantin &amp; Chaboo" baseAuthorityYear="2016" box="[1271,1414,1082,1107]" class="Insecta" family="Cantharidae" genus="Plectonotum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Plectonotum</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
Currently, it includes 21 species (
<bibRefCitation author="Delkeskamp, K." box="[1196,1414,1114,1139]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" refId="ref19204" refString="Delkeskamp, K. 1977. Coleopterorum Catalogus Supplementa, Cantharidae. 2. ed. The Hague, Dr W. Junk. Pars 165, fasc. 1, 485 p." type="book" year="1977">Delkeskamp, 1977</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Wittmer, W." box="[794,957,1146,1171]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" pagination="62 - 65" refId="ref19790" refString="Wittmer, W. 1980. 36. Beitrag zur Kenntnis der neotropischen Cantharidae (Col.). Mitteillungen der Entomologische Gesellschaft Basel, N. F., 30: 62 - 65." type="journal article" year="1980">Wittmer, 1980</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="21.[794,1419,762,1747]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">
The genus has never benefited from any revision.The following key is a first attempt toward an identification key, based on 
<typeStatus box="[953,1014,1242,1267]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">types</typeStatus>
and other material preserved in the collections of Wittmer (NHMB), Pic (MNHN) and some personal ones.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="21.[794,1419,762,1747]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">
This genus is not really homogeneous and the species can be separated into informal groups when a particular character is considered: a first group of species, already recognized by Wittmer, includes three species with a rough head surface, with wide areolar punctation; a group with a smooth and raised periphery of the pronotum; a group with modifications of the antennomeres of the males; other species with a lateral bead of the pronotum reduced to a small tuberosity of the anterior angles or without any bead. The distribution of this genus was known only from 
<collectingCountry box="[1099,1155,1658,1683]" name="Chile" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">Chile</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[1216,1329,1658,1683]" name="Argentina" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">Argentina</collectingCountry>
. Recent surveys bring to light two new species from central and north 
<collectingCountry box="[862,915,1722,1747]" name="Peru" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">Peru</collectingCountry>
, described below.
</paragraph>
